{"tid":2203221,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【Can Bank】證監與警方的MOU -散子","createTime":"2020-09-15T07:50:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T08:18:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e34d787420f94518922a538c62b574f93eae06b6","tid":2203221,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T07:50:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200915/N4B6U72BGNHEZBNM6L4NADUPWE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200915%2FN4B6U72BGNHEZBNM6L4NADUPWE%2F&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIuQoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=102daaca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200915%2FN4B6U72BGNHEZBNM6L4NADUPWE%2F&h=0954c104\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200915/N4B6U72BGNHEZBNM6L4NADUPWE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n【Can Bank】證監與警方的MOU -散子<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/V_ElesyzZ4CjWbcQc_2MDHnYCBA=/1280x883/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/I4IJS7WJKVH6REJ7BFFHTYTWWQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FV_ElesyzZ4CjWbcQc_2MDHnYCBA%3D%2F1280x883%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FI4IJS7WJKVH6REJ7BFFHTYTWWQ.jpg&h=46b92264&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■證監會與警方在2017年簽訂諒解備忘錄，當中清楚列明雙方的角色。 資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n證監會上周五回應警方高調調查壹傳媒（282）股價波動，甚少人提及警方與證監會之間的諒解備忘錄（MOU），此MOU是雙方在2017年簽訂，不妨看看在意向下雙方曾答應如何合作。<br />\n<br />\nMOU提到雙方的角色，警方是由《警務條例》賦予權力執行職務，而證監會的調查權則是來自《證券條例》；至於案件的分工，MOU就寫明如果警方認為有關犯罪或失當行為已經跌出其職權範圍，但可能跌入證監職能的話，可以將個案轉介，相反亦然；雙方更可以成立調查小組聯手調查案案件。<br />\n<br />\nMOU內對於向傳媒發放消息亦都有列明應該如何處理，雙方定期6個月開一次會，。。。。。。。。。。。警方代表是已退休的警務署助理處長（刑事）鍾兆揚，暫時未見有新接任人。<br />\n<br />\n根據新聞稿，證監仍然是希望可以根據MOU行事，換言之，在證監會中，這份MOU仍然存在，不知道警方是否一樣認為是仍然存在而已。<br />\n<br />\n散子<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/散子-257101397966975\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2F%E6%95%A3%E5%AD%90-257101397966975&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIuQoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=dc3b8d5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/散子-257101397966975</a>"},{"pid":"fc80cf3210afb6c6004702711fed6590a79235ad","tid":2203221,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T08:18:27.000Z","msg":"證監： 毒品調查科你唔識就唔好撈過界啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}